query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `tags` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `color` varchar(20) DEFAULT '#007AFF',
  `createdAt` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `userId` (`userId`)
);
